09:43.920 --> 09:44.887
- YEAH. THIS FEELS MOMENTOUS.

09:44.920 --> 09:47.332
- OH, GOD, I AM SO,
SO SORRY, MR. CARLSON.

09:47.370 --> 09:50.237
LOOK, SOMETIMES EMOTIONS
ARE SO HARD FOR MAX TO READ.

09:50.270 --> 09:52.067
YOU HAVE TO UNDERSTAND THAT,
YOU KNOW,

09:52.100 --> 09:53.419
