IF IT DIED IT WOULD BE...

10:18.300 --> 10:22.122
YOU KNOW WHAT, MAYBE WHAT
I CAN DO IS CALL THE PARENTS

10:22.170 --> 10:24.855
AND SOMETIMES ALL YOU NEED
IS A LITTLE COMMUNICATION

10:24.900 --> 10:26.652
AND JUST IT'LL SMOOTH
EVERYTHING OVER,

10:26.690 --> 10:28.203
AND IT'LL BE FINE. YOU'LL SEE.
- NOT NECESSARY.

10:28.240 --> 10:29.059
