- IT'LL BE FINE. GOOD.

10:29.110 --> 10:32.136
- BUT I WANT
TO MOVE MAX TO LAYOUT.

10:32.180 --> 10:34.102
- WELL, LAYOUT'S WHERE
YOU MOVE PICTURES AROUND.

10:34.150 --> 10:36.698
