SORT OF PUT 'EM ON PAPER.

10:36.730 --> 10:37.412
- DESIGN IS A HUGE
PART OF THE YEARBOOK.

10:37.460 --> 10:38.859
- RIGHT.

10:38.910 --> 10:40.878
I GET IT, BUT SEE,
MAX IS A PHOTOGRAPHER.

10:40.910 --> 10:43.140
LIKE, HE'S--
HE'S LOVING THIS SO MUCH.

10:43.190 --> 10:44.737
AND IT'S SO GOOD FOR HIM.
- MM-HMM.

10:44.780 --> 10:47.772
AND I GET THAT YOU WANT TO DO
WHAT'S BEST FOR YOUR KID.

10:47.810 --> 10:50.984
