10:51.020 --> 10:52.339
WHO WANT TO MAKE THIS
THE BEST YEARBOOK EVER.

10:52.370 --> 10:56.739
AND YEARBOOK IS ABOUT BEST HAIR
AND CUTEST COUPLE.

10:56.790 --> 10:58.234
- MM-HMM. I REMEMBER.
I WAS--I GET--

10:58.270 --> 11:01.751
- YEAH. GREAT.
MAX DOESN'T REALLY GET THAT.

