I JUST SAID.

12:09.210 --> 12:10.472
- YEAH, NO, I GUESS
I NEED TO TALK TO...

12:10.520 --> 12:12.033
- NO, YOU DON'T
NEED TO ANYTHING.

12:12.070 --> 12:14.277
- TALK TO AMBER WHEN I--
- NO, NO, NO, NO, PLEASE, I--

12:14.310 --> 12:15.516
- WHERE'S THE TOILET?
- WOULD BE BETTER IF YOU DID--

12:15.560 --> 12:17.107
UPSTAIRS.
- YEAH, YEAH.

