12:40.440 --> 12:42.067
I'M REALLY MISSING IT.
- MORE LUTE.

12:42.100 --> 12:44.546
- I JUST WANT IT TO ALMOST DROWN
OUT THE MARVIN GAYE SAMPLE.

12:44.590 --> 12:46.103
JUST ALMOST.

12:46.140 --> 12:48.449
- YOU WANT TO ALSO
