12:51.010 --> 12:53.592
I WANT IT TO BE, LIKE,
A SPLISH OF KANYE WEST,

12:53.630 --> 12:55.518
A SPLASH OF DAl-T PUNK,

12:55.560 --> 12:59.144
WITH A LITTLE SPRINKLE
OF T. REX ON THAT, BUT STILL US.

12:59.190 --> 13:02.944
- WELL, THOSE ARE A LITTLE BIT
CONFLICTING INGREDIENTS,

13:02.980 --> 13:04.845
BUT YEAH, I MEAN, I--
MAYBE IT'LL--

13:04.880 --> 13:06.871
- I JUST WANT THIS
TO SOUND LIKE

13:06.920 --> 13:08.808
NOTHING ANYONE'S
EVER HEARD BEFORE.

13:08.850 --> 13:11.978
- WE ARE ACCOMPLISHING THAT,
I CAN PROMISE YOU THAT.

13:12.030 --> 13:13.816
- HOW'S IT GOING?
- THANKS, MAN.

13:13.860 --> 13:14.679
PSSH.
[falsetto] MAGIC TIME.

13:14.720 --> 13:15.573
- YEAH? MAKING THE MAGIC?
ALL RIGHT.

13:15.620 --> 13:16.928
- YES, SIR.

13:16.960 --> 13:18.131
- GOING ALL RIGHT?

13:18.170 --> 13:21.139
- WE ARE GONNA TAKE
ANOTHER STAB AT HEAR ME NOW.

13:21.170 --> 13:22.444
- HEAR ME NOW?

13:22.490 --> 13:23.559
- YEAH, THAT'S WHAT
WE'RE FIXING TO DO NOW.

13:23.590 --> 13:25.319
- WE ALREADY RECORDED THAT.

13:25.350 --> 13:27.079
