WE ALREADY HAVE RECORDED.

13:27.110 --> 13:28.554
_ THAT'S RIGHT, BUT APPARENTLY,
ACCORDING TO THE ARTIST,

13:28.600 --> 13:30.522
IT HAD A STARTLING LACK
