GONNA GIVE IT TO THEM.

13:42.300 --> 13:44.154
- IT'S THEIR VISION--THEIR
VISION WITHIN REASON, OKAY?

13:44.200 --> 13:45.849
TIME IS MONEY.
BE A PRODUCER.

13:45.890 --> 13:48.302
- HEY, I AM AWARE OF THE NEW
PARADIGM, WHICH YOU CREATED...

13:48.340 --> 13:49.409
- OH, YOU ARE.

13:49.440 --> 13:51.089
- AND ITS FINANCIAL
CONSEQUENCES.

13:51.140 --> 13:52.061
SO I'M DOING WHAT I CAN.
- LET'S JUST KEEP IT MOVING.

13:52.100 --> 13:54.239
- I'M GONNA KEEP IT MOVING.
- ALL RIGHT.

13:54.280 --> 13:56.339
- [tuning lute]

13:56.380 --> 13:58.029
THE LUTE IS READY.

13:58.070 --> 13:59.549
- NICE.

13:59.590 --> 14:02.275
- YEAH, I USED THE 2.8 LENS,
WHICH SEEMS TO HAVE REALLY

14:02.320 --> 14:03.935
ENHANCED THE NATURAL LIGHT
COMING IN FROM THE WINDOW.

14:03.980 --> 14:04.799
- YEAH, IT REALLY KIND OF

14:04.840 --> 14:07.593
CAPTURES THE AGONY
OF HIGH SCHOOL.

14:07.630 --> 14:09.018
I REMEMBER THERE WAS ALWAYS

14:09.050 --> 14:10.017
SOMEBODY CRYING
ABOUT SOME STUFF.

14:10.050 --> 14:11.278
- HEY.

14:11.330 --> 14:13.150
HI, GUYS.
- OH, HEY, LOOK WHO'S HERE.

14:13.190 --> 14:14.225
- I STILL HAVE 17 MINUTES LEI-T.

