SHE'S FEELING IN THIS PHOTO.

14:41.500 --> 14:45.015
HOW DO YOU THINK
SHE FEELS RIGHT NOW HERE?

14:45.050 --> 14:46.324
- SAD.
- SAD. RIGHT.

14:46.360 --> 14:48.567
AND SOMETIMES
WHEN PEOPLE FEEL SAD,

14:48.610 --> 14:51.158
YOU KNOW, THEY WANT TO KEEP
THOSE EMOTIONS PRIVATE

14:51.200 --> 14:52.326
AND TO THEMSELVES.

14:52.370 --> 14:53.644
- THEN WHY IS SHE
DOING IT IN PUBLIC?

14:53.680 --> 14:54.840
- RIGHT. RIGHT. SHE WAS DOING IT
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE HALLWAY.

14:54.890 --> 14:57.506
- SOMETIMES WHEN PEOPLE EXPRESS
THEIR EMOTIONS IN PUBLIC

14:57.550 --> 15:00.542
DOESN'T MEAN THAT YOU'RE
ALLOWED TO TAKE THEIR PHOTOS.

15:00.580 --> 15:01.444
I MEAN, YOU HAVE TO
ASK PERMISSION, I THINK.

15:01.480 --> 15:03.584
- WHY? HANK SAYS
PHOTOGRAPHY IS ALL ABOUT

15:03.620 --> 15:06.589
TRYING TO CAPTURE REAL MOMENTS.
- I STAND BY THAT.

15:06.620 --> 15:07.416
- RIGHT. AND THAT'S
A REAL MOMENT.

15:07.450 --> 15:09.554
- CERTAIN PLACES
AND CERTAIN TIMES,

15:09.590 --> 15:11.410
THERE ARE, FOR REAL MOMENTS.

15:11.460 --> 15:13.382
BUT THIS WAS NOT ONE OF THEM.
- THAT'S ONE OF THOSE TIMES.

15:13.420 --> 15:16.423
THAT RIGHT THERE
IN THAT PHOTO, THAT'S--

15:16.460 --> 15:18.212
THAT'S ONE OF THOSE TIMES.

15:18.260 --> 15:19.943
- THAT'S A GOOD MOMENT.
- BUDDY,

15:19.980 --> 15:22.084
CAN YOU WAIT
IN THE CAR FOR ME?

15:22.120 --> 15:24.259
- NO, I STILL HAVE
15 MINUTES LEI-T.

15:24.300 --> 15:25.562
I HAD 17 MINUTES,
BUT THEN YOU WASTED TWO OF THEM.

15:25.610 --> 15:27.157
- YOU KNOW WHAT, MAD MAX,

15:27.200 --> 15:28.462
WE GO'ITA FINISH UP
THAT PICTURE IN THE DARKROOM.

15:28.510 --> 15:29.477
YOU WANT TO GET THAT?

15:29.510 --> 15:31.091
- OKAY.
- IF THAT'S OKAY.

15:31.130 --> 15:32.233
- YEAH, IT'S FINE.

15:32.270 --> 15:33.999
- I'LL BE THERE
IN A COUPLE MINUTES.

15:34.030 --> 15:36.373
- I CALL HIM MAD MAX.
I THINK HE LIKES IT.

15:36.410 --> 15:37.547
I CAN'T TELL.
- LISTEN, HANK, I, UM...

15:37.590 --> 15:41.686
I'M SO THANKFUL FOR YOU,
FOR WHAT YOU'RE DOING FOR MAX,

15:41.730 --> 15:45.723
BUT, YOU KNOW, I--
THAT PHOTO, IT'S NOT A JOKE.

15:45.770 --> 15:48.489
LIKE, IT'S GO'ITEN HIM--HE'S
IN SO MUCH TROUBLE FOR THAT.

15:48.530 --> 15:52.591
AND HE'S BEEN DEMOTED,
YOU KNOW, TO LAYOUT. LAYOUT.

