TOOK THE TIME
TO SEE THE SUNSET

40:15.170 --> 40:16.159
- MRS. BRAVERMAN.

40:16.200 --> 40:19.021
- RYAN.
- YEAH.

40:19.070 --> 40:20.583
- HI. COME ON IN.

40:20.620 --> 40:23.544
