MY DAD DIED WHEN I WAS 11

40:30.080 --> 40:32.833
AND MY MOM REMARRIED

40:32.870 --> 40:37.898
HALF A YEAR LATER
TO A GUY FROM WORK

40:37.950 --> 40:41.602
WHO WAS OKAY TO HER,
BUT THOUGHT CORPORAL PUNISHMENT

40:41.640 --> 40:44.529
WAS THE BEST WAY
TO HANDLE A WILD KID

40:44.580 --> 40:45.569
WHO WAS PISSED AS HELL
ABOUT LOSING HIS DAD.

40:45.610 --> 40:48.716
- OH, RYAN, I'M SO SORRY.

40:48.750 --> 40:50.889
- NO, NO, NO.
I DON'T NEED PITY, I'M JUST--

40:50.930 --> 40:54.024
I'M JUST--I'M JUST
TELLING YOU THE REASON

40:54.070 --> 40:55.207
WHY I LEI-T HOME
AS QUICK AS I DID

40:55.240 --> 40:56.821
AND NEVER LOOKED BACK,
NEVER WILL.

40:56.860 --> 40:58.202
- RYAN, YOU DON'T HAVE TO
GIVE ME AN EXPLANATION.

40:58.240 --> 41:00.583
- WELL, I WANT
TO GIVE YOU THE ANSWERS

41:00.630 --> 41:03.178
TO THE QUESTIONS
YOU KEEP ASKING, SO...

41:03.210 --> 41:06.099
NOT EVERYBODY
HAS A FAMILY LIKE YOURS.

41:06.150 --> 41:09.495
AND I KNOW THAT I MESSED UP.

41:09.530 --> 41:10.758
I KNOW THAT I DID SOME THINGS
THE LAST TIME I GOT BACK

41:10.810 --> 41:12.254
THAT SCARED YOU
AND THEY SHOULD HAVE.

41:12.290 --> 41:13.564
IT'S YOUR DAUGHTER.

41:13.600 --> 41:16.160
BUT I LOVE HER.

41:16.190 --> 41:19.671
I LOVE HER SO MUCH.

41:19.710 --> 41:23.669
AND I'M WORKING SO HARD
TO GET BETTER.

41:23.720 --> 41:25.506
AND I WANT TO BE WORTHY
OF YOUR FAMILY.

41:25.550 --> 41:27.689
I WANT TO BE WORTHY OF HER.

41:27.720 --> 41:29.267
AND I KNOW YOU THINK
THAT WE'RE RUSHING,

41:29.310 --> 41:32.962
WE'RE GOING
INTO THIS TOO FAST,

41:33.000 --> 41:35.036
BUT I CAN TELL YOU GREW UP
REAL FAST ON YOUR OWN.

41:35.070 --> 41:36.276
YOU GREW UP FAST
IN THE MILITARY.

41:36.320 --> 41:39.244
I KNOW WHAT I WANT.

41:39.280 --> 41:44.070
AND I WANT US TO START
OUR LIVES TOGETHER.

41:47.120 --> 41:50.840
- NICE SURPRISE
READY TO GROW...

41:50.880 --> 41:52.916
- OKAY.

